Winning numbers drawn in ‘All or Nothing Evening’ game
AUSTIN, Texas (AP) _ The winning numbers in Tuesday evening’s drawing of the Texas Lottery’s “All or Nothing Evening” game were:
01-03-04-06-11-14-16-17-18-20-22-24
(one, three, four, six, eleven, fourteen, sixteen, seventeen, eighteen, twenty, twenty-two, twenty-four)
